:: CC-Name [creation-page] {"position":"550,100","size":"100,100"}
<h1>Choose your Name</h1>\

//What is your name?//
<<textbox "$mc.name" "">>
<<button "Confirm">>
    <<if !$mc.name.trim()>>
        <<set $mc.name = "No-Name">>
    <</if>>
    <<goto "Index-CC">> 
<</button>>

Once you are set on a name you will be sent back to the menu of traits.


